data.description: Adorable ranch on tranquil cul-de sac in Driver Station community. This residence features a fantastic floor plan w foyer, a versatile flex space currently used as office (potentially a 4th BR), & inviting living room that opens to a covered rear patio & yard enclosed by privacy fence. The living room transitions into a stunning eat-in kitchen, boasting vinyl plank flooring, white subway tile backsplash, shaker cabinetry, a center island, granite countertops, SS appliances (approx. 5-6 yrs old), & pantry. Laundry / garage access conveniently located off kitchen. On the other end of the home, find two BR with ample closet space, a shared hallway bathroom, & a generously sized primary BR w walk-in closet & ensuite bathroom. Located in close proximity to parks, highways, restaurants, & entertainment, this immaculate single-floor home is ideal for any buyer seeking a low-maintenance, move-in ready property. LG Fridge in kitchen, W&D, hanging rack in garage & sec. cameras do not convey.
